title: Cannot log into new client

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: About 3 days before riot closed the transfers i transferred my account from EUNE to EUW and now whenever i try to log in on the new client it says my account has been transferred to another region. I have tried to log into every single region and i have even reinstalled league of legends and it still didn't work. Any one else have this problem? if so is there a fix?

replies.body: I took a look into this for you and it doesn't seem like the account was stuck between existence.  It appears to me that it successfully transferred over a while ago.  If you are still having an issue accessing the account, hit us up in a [support ticket](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/requests/new).  Our account team can look into this and see what's up.  Hang tight!
I sent a support ticket a couple days ago, still awaiting a reply but thank you.
